   "source": [
    "# `prune_branches`\n",
    "Removes dangling branches from a skeleton."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,

    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-04-25T01:56:28.229261Z",

    "import porespy as ps\n",
    "import scipy.ndimage as spim\n",

   "source": [
    "im = ps.generators.blobs(shape=[250, 250], blobiness=1, porosity=0.6)\n",
    "sk = skeletonize_3d(im)\n",
    "sk1 = ps.filters.prune_branches(sk)\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=[12, 6])\n",
    "ax[0].imshow(sk/im, interpolation='none', origin='lower')\n",
    "ax[0].axis(False)\n",
    "ax[1].imshow(sk1/im, interpolation='none', origin='lower')\n",
    "ax[1].axis(False);"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
